  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">TPF Turkey 2021 Wildfire Relief Fund</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">On July 28 and 29 more than 60 fires started in 21 cities in Turkey. As of July 30th, 14 of these fires (in Adana, Osmaniye, Mersin, Antalya, Mugla, Kayseri, and Manisa) are still not under control. The massive fires have been spreading due to high temperatures and winds. The fires are unprecedented in scope and impact. All donations to this fund will support wildfire relief and recovery efforts in Turkey.</narrative>
  </description>
